	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok, I know my message will probably get replied to like crazy, but, the thing I want to say here is, it seems like most of these posts are thinking of this item as a pal item.&nbsp;&nbsp;Think of having a SK that get mana back fast.  I mean, his life tap type spells alone would be great to do one after another without running out of mana.  Being that I do not find SKs to have much mana, and find mine runs out of mana on a regular basis, this item would be spectacular.  It would allow almost non-stop spells, and combined with his attacks and &quot;pacing&quot; the spells, your SK becomes the terror of Norrath.  Well folks, reply away...<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Who knows what evil lurks in the hearts of man.</td></tr>
